creator: UniQ Software
descriptionHtml:
Stylish text app for Your chatting needs 2020.

He have created a new fancy text maker to create some awesome and beautiful text for chat.

Main features of this text font style app 😍

You can make as many stylish text as you want using fancy text generator. Below are the major features of this app which makes this app really very useful in your daily life.

👉How can you use this Stylish fonts for WhatsApp

👉 Emoji letter maker :
You can create awesome letters with emoji face using this feature.

👉 Text repeater : You can repeat your text to impress someone else.

👉 Fancy text maker : You can share multiple faces of a text to your loved ones.


All three features of this app are on the main page. Using these features is really easy because these are combined with sliding pager. So, you don't need to open different activity for each feature. Just open the home page and slide to use all the features of this app.

🖌 Stylish fonts generator for for whatsapp

How to use this app to generate stylish text and use it every where?

Its really easy to get some awesome text by clicking generate button after downloading this stylish text app for whatsapp for free. For this just open the main page. On the home page and on the first page, you can see stylish text generator. Input your text in the box and click generate. Hurrah! Lots of cool text will be there. There is some option to share, copy and make it favourite. Sharing options include sharing direct to some major social media or  other apps.

How to add your fancy text to favourites inside text font style app 🧡

Using the tool fancy text generator to generate and after it, Adding your generated stylish text or chat style to favourites is very easy. When your fancy text is generated just click on arrow button on the right side. There you have more option which include add to favourite with heart button. Just click on it. To check your favourite fancy fonts just slide right or click of favourites. In order to remove anything from it, just click on remove button. Also, no need to use any  stylish font keyboard. Because this app enable you to create stylish fonts and many more. In order to know more about how to create stylish fonts just read the above topic.

😘 Using emoji letter maker for WhatsApp

Make your letter or word as emoji. To convert anything to emoji letter in text font style , this option is really useful. Just add any letter or word in the box and also put your desired emoji to the box under it. Click generate to get a beautiful emoji text. You can generate as many emoji letter or chat style as you want. There is not any limit.

✍ Impressive stylish text repeater

There is another function which you must like. Except fancy text generator, another feature is Stylish Text repeater and it is the the third option. It is used to repeat any word or sentence in a single click. In order to use this function you have to put your choice to input text box. After adding, just add the limit you want and click generate. Done! you can see Repeated text in single different line or same line. Just click on share button to share stylish text with your friends and impress them.

Another cool feature of stylish fonts app is user friendly and clear behaviour for creating text styles. Users can easy share or send all of the generated stylish fonts to their family or friends. Also, while chatting, you can send these chat style and impress everyone.

Note: Names used in this description are for demonstration purpose. All names are copyright to their owners like WhatsApp is copyright to WhatsApp Inc.
